commerce-admin','2020-12-11 01:34:46',NULL,0,'plain','',0),(19,'wc-admin-store-notice-giving-feedback-2','info','en_US','Give feedback','Now that you’ve chosen us as a partner, our goal is to make sure we\'re providing the right tools to meet your needs. We\'re looking forward to having your feedback on the store setup experience so we can improve it in the future.','info','{}','unactioned','woocommerce-admin','2020-12-11 01:34:46',NULL,0,'plain','',0),(20,'wc-admin-insight-first-sale','survey','en_US','Did you know?','A Quản lý bán hàng powered store needs on average 31 days to get the first sale. You\'re on the right track! Do you find this type of insight useful?','info','{}','unactioned','woocommerce-admin','2020-12-11 01:34:46',NULL,0,'plain','',0),(21,'wc-admin-real-time-order-alerts','info','en_US','Get real-time order alerts anywhere','Get notifications about store activity, including new orders and product reviews directly on your mobile devices with the Woo app.','info','{}','unactioned','woocommerce-admin','2020-12-11 01:34:46',NULL,0,'plain','',0),(22,'wc-admin-manage-orders-on-the-go','info','en_US','Manage your orders on the go','Look for orders, customer info, and process refunds in one click with the Woo app.','info','{}','unactioned','woocommerce-admin','2020-12-11 01:34:46',NULL,0,'plain','',0),(23,'wc-admin-home-screen-feedback','info','en_US','Help us improve the Quản lý bán hàng Home screen','We\'d love your input to shape the future of the Quản lý bán hàng Home screen together. Feel free to share any feedback, ideas or suggestions that you have.','info','{}','unactioned','woocommerce-admin','2020-12-22 21:32:09',NULL,0,'plain','',0),(24,'your-first-product','info','en_US','Your first product','That’s huge! You’re well on your way to building a successful online store — now it’s time to think about how you’ll fulfill your orders.<br /><br />Read our shipping guide to learn best practices and options for putting together your shipping strategy. A